{"tid":1399342,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"集中返五大訴求。唔好比人帶風向去港獨！","createTime":"2019-08-03T06:33:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T13:13:33.000Z","uid":267556,"like":16,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"866d310531df9272cf7b5604368dd519aad66384","tid":1399342,"uid":267556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:33:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">5大訴求都未得，你搞咁多做乜！？<br />\n警狗你都未搞掂，水炮車都冇對策，你搞乜柒港獨！？<br />\n有真普選先啦！<br />\n集中返5大訴求先啦！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n中央一路都想介入平亂，冇港獨，冇得入。因為干預特區內政，破壞一國兩制！<br />\n港獨就係分裂國家，出錢出軍都合理！<br />\n佢地想左好耐架啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1321544/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1321544/page/1</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><br />\n光復香港！ 時代革命！！<br />\n8.5 三罷！！<br />\n成立獨立調查委員會，改革監警會！改革投訴課！！<br />\n立即實行雙普選<br />\n釋放義士</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"a2c624bb97ba92754926bd0f942e2e799a19f492","tid":1399342,"uid":267556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:37:34.000Z","msg":"呢個POST的71樓講左我的諗法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1320094/page/1?post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1320094/page/1?post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n事有分先後!<br />\n搞掂左1,2,3, 你講乜都得啦真係!!!"},{"pid":"91038cd64f2641fe37ca96d25ad503fd6d79ffb5","tid":1399342,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:47:11.000Z","msg":"快點出軍攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e811dcc9a1b486caf8406443aa1598da2e38c651","tid":1399342,"uid":267556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91038cd64f2641fe37ca96d25ad503fd6d79ffb5","tid":1399342,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:47:11.000Z","msg":"快點出軍攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hk